BUSYBOX NEWS FROM BUSYBOX.NET
=============================

The Software Freedom Conservancy (sfconservancy.org) acts as the GPL enforcement
agent for various BusyBox copyright holders. If you wish to report a GPL violation
on BusyBox, please write to gpl@busybox.net.

27 September 2024 -- BusyBox 1.37.0 (unstable)

    Sizes of busybox-1.36.0 and busybox-1.37.0
        (with equivalent config, static musl build):

   text	   data	    bss	    dec	    hex	filename
1022792	    559	   4988	1028339	  fb0f3	busybox-1.36.0/busybox
1024327	    559	   4988	1029874	  fb6f2	busybox-1.37.0/busybox

