     Changes since previous release:

    New applets:
    - conspy by Pascal Bellard (pascal.bellard AT ads-lu.com),
    - rev by Marek Polacek (mmpolacek AT gmail.com),
    - ubiattach,ubidetach by Baruch Siach (baruch AT tkos.co.il),
