    Top 10 stack users:   busybox-1.8.2:                busybox-1.9.0:
    input_tab             10428  echo_dg                4116
    umount_main            8252  bb_full_fd_action      4112
    rtnl_talk              8240  discard_dg             4096
    xrtnl_dump_filter      8240  echo_stream            4096
